{
  "stem": "9446.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mark, M-A-R-K, Laski-- spelled L-A-S-K-I.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "September 12, 1919.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "76.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Warsaw, Poland.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If it is all right with you, I'd like to throw in a little bit of a background on Poland at that time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was born right one year after the end of the First World War, which ended in 1918 with the.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Poland was a very unfortunate place to be born in, especially for a Jewish person.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] It was a period of brief independence for Poland-- from 1918, after the war ended, until 1939 when the other one started between Poland and Germany.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Those were the 20 good years for me-- good in a sense that Poland was a free country at that time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'd like to also mention [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the fact this is the most tragic part of my childhood.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother died about a week or two weeks after my birth as a result of the blood infection. 76 years ago, there was no penicillin.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was no way of saving her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Frankly, [SIGHS] I only wish [INAUDIBLE] all the Nazis I should say to feel the-- feel the experience of not being able to say 'mother' forever.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because that's-- that is something I never could say.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father, as a result of this tragedy, was nearly suicidal.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He survived only because of the consolation he received from his sisters and brother.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he managed to somehow go on with life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I personally never stopped feeling guilty about it, because she died as a result of my birth.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that feeling of guilt still stays with me even today after all those years.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Now I was raised by my father, [INAUDIBLE], and also by one of my aunts, Aunt Helen.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
